    dc:description "FIGURES 9–12. Examples of the symmetrical setal pattern on frons and vertex in representatives of the 'Afroeudesis lineage' (insertions of setae, including those broken off, marked by circles).Meridaphes venezolanus (9); Stenichnoconnus huijbregtsensis (10); Pseudoraphes minor (11); Afroeudesis (Nanoscydmus) baoshana (12)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3234302/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

